    <sense group="1" n="1" name="a significant link or association between things" type="Event">
        <commentary>
            CONNECTION[+relation][+association][+significant]
            Any relationship or non-physical link between two things.
            Can refer to electronic signals.
        </commentary>
        <examples>
            The connection between church and state is inescapable.
            There was a connection between eating that pickle and having that bad dream.
            What's your connection to John?
            Only a brilliant detective could find connections among the evidence.    
        </examples>
        <mappings>
            <wn version="3.0">1</wn>
            <omega/><pb/>
        </mappings>
        <SENSE_META clarity=""/>
    </sense>
    
