    <sense group="1" n="4" name="Act of connecting" type="Event">
        <commentary>
            CONNECTION[+event][+joining]
            The act of bringing two or more things together, either physically or non-physically.  
        </commentary>
        <examples>
            Classical conditioning is the process of learning by connection.
            The connection of the two railroad lines would make transportation much easier.
            John's first connection to the Internet occurred yesterday at noon.
            I recall the connection of your fist and my chin as a painful event.
        </examples>
        <mappings>
            <wn version="3.0">1</wn>
            <omega/><pb/>
        </mappings>
        <SENSE_META clarity=""/>
    </sense>
    
